11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 37A O.S. 2021, Section 2-129, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 2-129. A. A charitable auction or charitable alcoholic
15 beverage event license may be issued to a charitable organization
16 exempt from taxation under Section 501(c)(3), (4) 501(c)(4), (5)
17 501(c)(5), (6) 501(c)(6), (7) 501(c)(7), (8) 501(c)(8), (9)
18 501(c)(9), (10) 501(c)(10) or (19) 501(c)(19) of the United States
19 Internal Revenue Code of 1986, as amended. The charitable alcoholic
20 beverage event license shall authorize the holder thereof to conduct
21 a wine, spirit and/or beer event which may consist of one or more of
22 a wine, spirit and/or beer-tasting event, a wine, spirit and/or beer
23 dinner event or a wine, spirit and/or beer auction, which may be
